---
import SvgWebsite from '@components/Icon/Website.astro'
import SvgDot from '@components/Icon/Dot.astro'
---

<div class="website-container">
    <section
    class="a-website"
    >
        <div class="svg">
            <SvgWebsite/>
        </div>
        <a class="code" href="https://zongyuanlu.github.io/">zongyuanlu.github.io</a>
        <h3 class="heading-3">Welcome to my personal website~</h3>
        <p class="body">
            Now I am working in Xiaomi Corp. as a software developer.
            <br>
            <br>
            Jul. 2022 - now, Xiaomi Corp. SDE in Smartphone dept.
            <br>
            <br>
            2022年7月至今，在小米手机测试部任职软件开发工程师。
        </p>
        <h3 class="heading-4">Education</h3>
        <p class="resume">
            Aug. 2021 - Jul. 2022, City University of Hong Kong, Msc in Computer Science.
            <br>
            <br>
            2021年8月至2022年7月， 香港城市大学计算机理学硕士。
            <br>
            <br>
            Sept. 2017 - Jul. 2021, South China University of Technology, BEng in Information Secirity.
            <br>
            <br>
            2017年9月至2021年七月，华南理工大学信息安全工学学士。
        </p>
    </section>
</div>

<style>
.website-container{
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1em;
}
.a-website{
    background-image: linear-gradient(83.21deg,#3245FF 0%,#B845ED 100%);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    color:  rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    position: relative;
    border-radius: var(--base-radius);
    margin: 1em 0;
    padding: 1.5em;
}
.a-website:nth-child(2){
    background-image: linear-gradient(247.23deg,#4AF2C8 0%,#2F4CB3 100%);
}
.a-website:nth-child(3){
    background-image: linear-gradient(66.77deg,#D83333 0%,#F041FF 100%);
}
.a-website .code{
    font-family: "MD IO 0.5",md-io-fallback,monospace;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
}
.a-website .svg{
    position: absolute;
    top: 2em;
    right: 1em;
}
.a-website h3{
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 2em;
    margin: 1em 0 0.5em;
}
</style>